A cyberpunk-style digital illustration depicting a glowing orange JavaScript logo symbol floating as a holographic core at the center of a vast server room. Towering black server racks stretch into the distance, their surfaces covered with pulsing neon circuit patterns in electric blue and purple. Data streams visualized as luminous particles flow from the central JavaScript emblem outward in all directions, connecting to the surrounding infrastructure like digital synapses. The atmosphere is hazy with volumetric light, casting dramatic shadows. Multiple translucent holographic screens hover in the air displaying abstract code patterns and data visualizations. The ceiling above reveals exposed industrial piping and cables wrapped in LED strips. The overall mood is mysterious and powerful, suggesting hidden computational force operating behind the scenes of the digital world.
